room_title: Escape room "Vendetta" by LOCKED in New York
room_description: Your team is part of the Mobinos family of the “CosaNostra”, who is in search of the secret office of Sam Biancana, a famous banker of the Biancana family in New York. After 50 years (at midnight) the unclaimed $300,000,000 kept in a secret bank account (unknown to the Mobinos) is going to turn hands to the Biancanas. The time is 11:00 p.m., the bank is closed and you have 60 minutes to break into a laser protected office to unlock the bank account and bring back the money to your family. Can you make it in 60 minutes?
